title: Fairy Tail OST Collection - Complete as of 21st August 2016
description:
Complete OST collection for Fairy Tail up to August 2016.
Contains OST Volumes 1-6 (Vol 4, 5 and 6 are 2 disc sets)
Includes Fairy Tail Original Sound Collection Volume 1 and 2 (OST Vol. 5 and 6)
OST for Fairy Tail Houou no Miko (aka Fairy Tail the Movie: The Phoenix Princess)
All character songs 
All opening songs, all ending songs.

Good quality.  OST Volumes 1-6 have cover art.

This is an updated version of the Torrent available here (https://thepiratebay.org/torrent/12096544/Fairy_Tail_OST_Collection_-_Complete_as_of_6th_July_2015)

The new addition from the earlier torrent is Fairy Tail Original Sound Collection - Volume 2 (OST Vol 6.) that was released on July 15 2016
